# Haversine-like great-circle distance (integer approx using milli-degrees).
*hav(lat1 as i64, lon1 as i64, lat2 as i64, lon2 as i64) returns i64
    dx is lat2 - lat1
    dy is lon2 - lon1
    sq is dx * dx + dy * dy
    if sq equals 0
        return 0
    s is 1
    i is 0
    while i < 30
        s is (s + sq / s) / 2
        i is i + 1
    s

*main
    log hav(0, 0, 3000, 4000)
